8, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah inhabit Your cities through him and give life to Your servants due to him for surely You have said and Your word is truth, \"Corruption will become rampant in land and on sea because of the evil which men's hand have earned\" Then O Allah manifest for us Your slave and the son of Your Prophet's daughter, whose name is the same as that of Your messenger, so that nothing from falsehood is victorious except that he tears them (falsehood) to pieces, establishes the truth and the truth confirms him.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ اَرِنِيْ الطَّلْعَةَ الرَّشِيْدَةَ وَالْغُرَّةَ الْحَمِيْدَةَ، وَاكْحُلْ بَصَرِيْ ‏بِنَظْرَةٍ مِنِّيْ اِلَيْهِ، وَعَجِّلْ فَرَجَهُ، وَسَهِّلْ مَخْرَجَهُ۔ اَللّٰهُمَّ اشْدُدْ اَزْرَهُ، وَقَوِّ ظَهْرَهُ، وَطَوِّلْ عُمْرَهُ، وَاعْمُرِ اللّٰهُمَّ بِهِ ‏بِلَادَكَ، وَاَحْيِ بِهِ عِبَادَكَ، فَاِنَّكَ قُلْتَ وَقَوْلُكَ الْحَقُّ (ظَهَرَ الْفَسَادُ فِي الْبَرِّ وَالْبَحْرِ بِمَا كَسَبَتْ اَيْدِي النَّاسِ)۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "Arab